#- Foreward§0
§0Dear Reader,§0
§0Over these few months of Regency, Verda has seen much growth and joy. However, I have seen many newfriends go inactive, oldfriends leave, and many a raider. Only through persistence, 
#- honor, and orthodoxy could Verda persist. 
